00:13:04.170 --> 00:13:08.319
of rejection from a publishing company. Ethan
suddenly shows up, and after he gets a copy

00:13:08.319 --> 00:13:12.569
of Gerald's book, Thomas expresses his admiration
for him for not running away. They then do

00:13:12.569 --> 00:13:15.899
some catching up in the park, where Thomas
tells Ethan that Mimi has finally moved to

00:13:15.899 --> 00:13:20.959
Croatia. When Thomas asks if he still speaks
with Johanna, Ethan says he doesn't anymore.

00:13:20.959 --> 00:13:24.559
He then asks about Judith, and Thomas is delighted
to tell him that she's finally quit smoking

00:13:24.559 --> 00:13:28.449
and started writing for ARTnews again. Thomas
also adds that Judith has a date later in

00:13:28.449 --> 00:13:32.470
the evening, and Ethan says that's good for
her. After they part ways, Thomas goes to

00:13:32.470 --> 00:13:44.470
Gerald's book-reading event, where he sees
his mother happily listening to the man she

00:13:44.470 --> 00:13:44.959
loves.

